name: Orchard Designs

overview:
Orchard Designs is a fast growing internet marketing agency near Cleveland, Ohio. Started in 2004 as a freelance web design business for Brian Petti, a veteran website developer and search expert, Orchard Designs has blossomed into a profitable and strong business, headquartered in Mentor, Ohio with over 50 active clients nationwide.

Orchard Designs provides search engine optimization, website design, custom web application development, e-commerce, web video production, web video seo, email marketing and landing page development and optimization.

For more information, please contact Brian Petti at info@orcharddesigns.com
